erver())` works because NestJS creates an HTTP server internally. Socket.io atta
ches to the same server. But without `listen()`, the server might not be fully s
et up for Socket.io.\n\nLet me try a different approach. In NestJS, `app.init()`
should be enough for the IoAdapter to set up Socket.io on the HTTP server. Then 
